J2EE/Websphere Developer - 6 mth contract (Markham?)

I am looking for a J2EE/Websphere Developer who has experience with Windows, UNIX, DB2 and SQL and experience with performance testing tools such as Rational Performance Tester and Borland SilkPerformer is desirable.  Experience with Eclipse or developing Eclipse plug-ins is also an advantage.

This is a 6 month contract to start, location in North-East Toronto. This is in the early phases to develop a multi-channel data centre application (call centre software).

Natalie Yacht
